# Knowledge Graph Instances
# =============================================================================

# --- KOS Concepts (explicitly defined for completeness, though often external) ---
# These are examples of how the KOS concepts would be defined if they were part of this graph.
# For the purpose of this exercise, we assume they exist at the specified URIs.
